title: Sly + The Family Stone - Live at Fillmore East 1968 (2015) 24-96
description:
A four-disc set of previously unreleased live performances, featuring four energetic shows from the legendary New York venue.

Sly & The Family Stone - Live at the Fillmore East October 4th & 5th 1968
Label: Epic/Legacy 
Format: WEB, 34 files FLAC, Album, 24bit 96kHz HDtracks
Released: 2015
Recorded live at the Fillmore East, NYC October 4th & 5th 1968
Genre: Soul, Funk, R&B
